<section id="scenarios-intro">
<title>Introduction</title>

<para>
The Inca components can be arranged in many ways in order to satisfy the needs
of a variety of different organizations.  The following usage scenarios show
some of the possible arrangements as well as provides explanations.
</para>

<para>
In every case it is true that each resource has at least on Reporter Manager
and that a Reporter Manager knows and trusts only a single Reporter Agent.
The Reporter Manager can know and trust several Depots but only Depots in the
same VO as its trusted Reporter Agent.
</para>

<note><title>Depot Representation in this section</title><para>
In this entire section a group of depots that exist within a single VO are
represented as a single Depot.  Multple Depots may be used for reliability as
well as for scalability, but in order to simplify the diagrams they are not
shown here.
</para>
</note>

</section>
